snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythmic Adventure Pack – Announcement Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Drum to save the world in two great RPG adventures when Taiko no Tatsujin: Rhythmic Adventure Pack comes to Nintendo Switch Holiday 2020!
